{"tid":2131752,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有市民入社區中心午膳時拉低口罩聊天被勸喻返回座位","createTime":"2020-07-30T05:04:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T05:29:21.000Z","uid":60281,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c31ff8c9161d87e03b798e88aa607d95052cae05","tid":2131752,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T05:04:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n梁顯利油麻地社區中心朝早11時開門後，有數位市民攜外賣入內進食，包括一些地盤工人。本台記者自備午餐入內，有職員量體溫及提供酒精搓手液。進入社區中心後，內有18張長枱供市民使用，枱與枱之間相隔1.5米，每張枱中間有紙板分隔，每張枱只有一支酒精搓手液，兩人共用，亦有人要到隔離枱借用搓手液。<br />\n<br />\n現場有市民拉低口罩後，離開座椅，與友人近距離聊天，有職員上前勸喻他們返回座位。亦有市民無戴口罩離開座位，有職員立刻上前阻止，指離開座位時必須戴上口罩。用膳市民離開後，有職員即時用清潔劑消毒和抹枱。<br />\n<br />\n19間社區中心在上午11時至下午3時開放。中心外張貼告示，提醒市民要自備食物、飲料和餐具，中心不會提供飲用水，市民除了進食期間，其他時間必須配戴口罩。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540758-20200730.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540758-20200730.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhPMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=45011217\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540758-20200730.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=3cf0b01f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540758-20200730.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"c8c0ad12eaa12eec1adaa0ee637fb65d2448d2ca","tid":2131752,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T05:05:40.000Z","msg":"監獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eac35952600e747c2a763bab06bc810bebf9c1b9","tid":2131752,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T05:14:53.000Z","msg":"驚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ec6286133dcc986ecd107f42eb41a1aa434913c","tid":2131752,"uid":106633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T05:16:24.000Z","msg":"菜 雞翼 飯 汁"},{"pid":"e6ce1d477115806494f8e2e3e5ae88b5f539a951","tid":2131752,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T05:16:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XeADPyK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXeADPyK.gif&h=675635f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2dcd06926eb46fac8bea485558893b4923a0d751","tid":2131752,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T05:17:54.000Z","msg":"水飯房？"},{"pid":"6d0a571f449e76b12b2ffb3c2c4f697c6a7b1632","tid":2131752,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T05:18:41.000Z","msg":"廢老又爆武肺"},{"pid":"e31fe813a5c0322faa3528d4fdaceb72e8f4dfcb","tid":2131752,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T05:19:27.000Z","msg":"監獄飯堂咁cls"},{"pid":"34344a9d5f7aad644f8d251bf3315352459c88b3","tid":2131752,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T05:29:21.000Z","msg":"好心佢攞支漂白水噴壺係枱度啦<br />\n上手食完，下手點清潔翻個隔版？"}]}